<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="above-adv">above <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əˈbʌv/    美 /əˈbʌv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(空间) 在上面；(数量等) 以上：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>children aged 12 <strong>and above</strong> 
12岁以及12岁以上的儿童</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My room is just above. 
我的房间就在上面。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>上述的；在上文：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I hope what’s mentioned above might be helpful. 
我希望上述内容会有帮助。</p></div></div>